docstring.long_description: This allows supporting a wide range of deep learning frameworks and hardware platforms.
docstring.short_description: Load a serialized ONNX model and uses it to make predictions using ONNX Runtime.

parameters.name: file_path
parameters.description: Path to a ONNX model to load and use for prediction.

parameters.name: default
parameters.description:
The input tensor to use for prediction.
For now, only a single input tensor is supported.
Note that the input tensor shape is not checked against the model's input shape.

returns.name: Vector
returns.description:
The predictions made by the ONNX model.
For now, only a single output tensor is supported.
